title: Night Monster (1942) 72min.DVDRip Ralph Morgan Universal Studios
description:
Night Monster:     

A creepy story of murder and revenge made by Universal Studios during the peak of their "classic horror" production days.

Kurt Ingston, a rich recluse, invites the doctors who left him a bitter & hopeless 
cripple to his desolate mansion in the swamps. One by one they meet horrible deaths. 	

Stars: Ralph Morgan, Lionel Atwill, Leif Erickson

             ...Bela Lugosi, in a very small role ..ARRGHH!
